This is a golang project using Cairo to generate some of the figures for use in the book.

Requirements:

1. Install golang from https://golang.org/
2. Install direnv from https://direnv.net/
3. Install `go-cairo` from `https://github.com/bit101/go-cairo` (can use `go get github.com/bit101/go-cairo`)
4. Install `blgo` from `https://github.com/bit101/blgo` (can use `go get github.com/bit101/blgo`)
5. Edit `main.go` to uncomment which image(s) you want to generate.
6. go run main.go
